Steps:
--- STOREFRONT (setup) ---
[NAV] Sign in at {{FRONT_URL}}; navigate to wedding cake PDP
[ACT] Select Base, Creme, Message options; do NOT fill Custom text required field
[ACT] Note the lineItemId from URL (?lineItemId=<UUID>) for use in the mutation
--- GRAPHQL ---
[NAV] Navigate to {{BACK_URL}}/ui/graphiql
[AUTH] Open HTTP Headers panel; enter: { "Authorization": "Bearer <token from storefront session>" }
[GQL] Type the following mutation (omitting Custom text required section from configurationSections):
mutation ChangeCartConfigured($command: InputChangeCartConfiguredItemType!) {
  changeCartConfiguredItem(command: $command) {
    items { id }
    validationErrors { errorCode errorMessage }
  }
}
[VAR] Set variables: { "command": { "storeId": "{{STORE_ID}}", "userId": "{{USER_ID}}", "currencyCode": "{{CURRENCY_CODE}}", "lineItemId": "<lineItemId from precondition>", "configurationSections": [ { "sectionId": "@td(CFG_023_SECTIONS.Base)", "value": { "productId": "<baseOptionProductId>", "quantity": 1 } }, { "sectionId": "@td(CFG_023_SECTIONS.Creme)", "value": { "productId": "<cremeOptionProductId>", "quantity": 1 } }, { "sectionId": "@td(CFG_023_SECTIONS.Message)", "value": { "productId": "<messageOptionProductId>", "quantity": 1 } } ] } }
[ACT] Click Execute (Play button)
[READ] Inspect response — record validationErrors[] and errors[] content

Test_Data:
store={{FRONT_URL}}
backUrl={{BACK_URL}}
productId=@td(CFG_CONDITIONAL_BIKE.id)
